		<div id="comment_body_64157069">For real.  And I think the real solution will be so simple, people will be slapping their foreheads for centuries.  Might as well try to reverse-engineer the forehead-slapping.  And to me, MOND and stuff like it seems to fit that bill.</div>
	</div>

